#: ../../language/error_codes/E4037.md:1
msgid "E4037"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4037.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `pkg_not_imported`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`pkg_not_imported`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4037.md:5
msgid "Cannot perform action: package is not imported."
msgstr "无法完成操作：包未导入。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4037.md:7
msgid ""
"Some language features require an explicit package import because the "
"compiler needs runtime support from that package. For example, `async fn "
"main` and `async test` require `moonbitlang/async`."
msgstr "有些语言特性需要显式导入包，因为编译器需要该包提供运行时支持。例如，`async fn main` 和 `async test` 需要 `moonbitlang/async`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4037.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4037.md:13
msgid ""
"async fn main {\n"
"//^~~~~\n"
"// Error: Cannot use `async fn main`: package moonbitlang/async is not "
"imported.\n"
"  ()\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4037.md:17
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4037.md:19
msgid ""
"Import the required package if you intend to use the feature. If you do "
"not need the feature, remove the construct that requires the package."
msgstr "如果你确实需要使用该特性，请导入所需的包。如果不需要该特性，请移除依赖该包的语法结构。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4037.md:22
msgid ""
"fn main {\n"
"  ()\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
